ommerce-Price-currencySymbol\">&#36;</span>138.00</bdi></span><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Price range: &#36;48.00 through &#36;138.00</span></span>\n\n\t<div class=\"wd-add-btn wd-add-btn-replace\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t<a href=\"https://goearthward.com/product/natural-pyrite-heart/\" aria-describedby=\"woocommerce_loop_add_to_cart_link_describedby_21482\" data-quantity=\"1\" class=\"button product_type_variable add_to_cart_button add-to-cart-loop\" data-product_id=\"21482\" data-product_sku=\"\" aria-label=\"Select options for &ldquo;Natural Pyrite Heart&rdquo;\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"wd-action-icon\"><span class=\"wd-check-icon\"></span></span><span class=\"wd-action-text\">Select options</span></a>\t<span id=\"woocommerce_loop_add_to_cart_link_describedby_21482\" class=\"screen-reader-text\">\n\t\tThis product has multiple variants. The options may be chosen on the product page\t</span>\n\t</div>\n\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQ About Crystals for Confidence</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Can crystals give me confidence?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Not directly. Crystals can&#8217;t grant confidence. Many people use them as tangible cues before a hard moment; the confidence itself comes from preparation and practice, not the stone.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Are crystals scientifically proven to boost confidence?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">No. There is no clinical evidence that crystals increase confidence. Any felt benefit usually comes from the ritual of pausing and setting an intention, not a proven effect of the stone.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Which crystal is best for confidence before a presentation or speech?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Tiger eye and carnelian — tiger eye for steady self-belief, carnelian for the push to start strong.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What is the best crystal for confidence after a setback?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Aventurine and citrine — aventurine for the optimism to try again, citrine for a warmer self-regard.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Which crystal helps me speak up more?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Carnelian and pyrite — carnelian for the courage to act, pyrite for bold, deliberate words.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How should I cleanse confidence crystals?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Smoke (sage, palo santo), sound (singing bowl), or moonlight work for most stones. Pyrite is metallic and can tarnish if damp — wipe it dry.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What is the best crystal bracelet for confidence?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">A tiger eye bracelet is the most common first choice — durable, widely available, and easy to wear as a steady cue to stand firm.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Explore More Crystal Guides</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"/crystals-for-courage/\">Crystals for Courage</a></li><li><a href=\"/crystals-for-motivation/\">Crystals for Motivation</a></li><li><a href=\"/crystals-for-success/\">Crystals for Success</a></li><li><a href=\"/crystals-for-communication/\">Crystals for Communication</a></li><li><a href=\"/crystals-for-self-love/\">Crystals for Self-love</a></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Confidence is built by doing the thing — and a real stone in your pocket can be a steady cue to take the step. Start with one and let practice do the rest. For more, explore <a href=\"/personal-empowerment/\">Personal Empowerment</a>.</p>\n",
